body: The first question is what is truly his original gender. Now, I believe that he was originally a male and I have some reasons as to why I believe that. The first reason is that on one of the pages where he was a female, he said: “this skirt wasn’t this long” as if he wasn’t accustomed to it. You may be thinking, “Hey but what if she is just disoriented after having such a realistic and weird dream?” This brings me to my next point. When I have dreams, I often forget the contents maybe 10 minutes after I have them. I also do not believe it is real for more than 10 seconds even if I do remember it vividly. The tone that he used to say that his maid uniform wasn’t of someone who just had a weird dream but of someone with implanted memories. This is evident because if it were to just be a dream, he would most likely say something like wasn’t i supposed to be a butler? Why are these maid uniforms here? He would then quickly remember that he is in fact a maid.
